==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Commensurately
<hw>Com*men"su*rate*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a
commensurate manner; so as to be equal or proportionate;
adequately.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>With equal measure or extent.</def>
<rj><au>Goodwin.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Commensurateness</ent>⟦br⟧
